SUMMARY: Making Gourd Rain Sticks
DESCRIPTION:Learn how to make a musical rain stick from a long-handled go
 urd and practice many gourd-crafting techniques such as pyrography\, etch
 ing\, alcohol ink and acrylic painting\, etc as we embellish our rain sti
 cks in bright colors\, geometric designs\, spirit-animals\, etc. We are t
 he Bloomington Patch of the Indiana Gourd Society meeting monthly on the 
 3rd Tuesday from 5:30pm-7:30pm. Newcomers are always welcome and attendan
 ce is free! For more information contact: igs.rgolson@aol.com mailto:igs.
 rgolson@aol.com \, or text 970-628-6864.
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Class,Free,Workshop
