SUMMARY: "High School Art Show" by young\, local talent
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Pillar Arts Alliance Center this February as w
 e celebrate the creativity of Bloomington’s high school artists.\n\nThis 
 special exhibition features an inspiring range of student work\, from vib
 rant watercolors and detailed drawings to imaginative collages and mixed 
 media pieces. The variety of styles and perspectives highlight the talent
  and creativity in our local schools.\n\nWe also hope you’ll join us for 
 the opening reception on Sunday\, February 1 from 3–5 PM. It’s a great op
 portunity to support young artists\, explore the exhibition\, and celebra
 te the next generation of creatives in our community!
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Free,In-Person,Gallery,Visual-Arts
