SUMMARY: "America the Beautiful" a membership and benefit art show by the
  Bloomington Watercolor Society
DESCRIPTION:Come see the beautiful watercolor artworks of Bloomington Wat
 ercolor Society at The Vault at Gallery Mortgage. Our works this year wil
 l be encompassing the theme "America the Beautiful". The artists will dis
 play their interpretations of America's beauty over the last 250 years in
  original watercolor paintings.\n\nTwo receptions will be held:\n\nFriday
 \, February 6\, 2026 Opening Day of Show & Reception at Gallery Mortgage 
 5-8pm\n\nAnd\n\nFriday\, March 6\, 2026 March Reception at Gallery Mortga
 ge 5-8 PM\n\nThe Vault at Gallery Mortgage is located at:\n\n\n121 E. 6th
  Street\nBloomington\, IN 47408\n\nRegular Gallery hours will be 9am – 5p
 m Monday – Friday through March 27th.\n\nA portion of sales will benefit 
 Teachers' Warehouse.
