SUMMARY: "Outside\, Inside\, In Between" by Anne-Karine Bley Reception
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Pillar Arts By Hand for this February's Arts Miles
 ' Gallery Walk!\n\nThis month we are proud to feature "Outside\, Inside\,
  In Between" by talented local artist\, Anne-Karine Bley.\n\nThe exhibit 
 invites the attendees on a journey through different spaces and perspecti
 ves—from the expansive external world\, to the intimate internal space of
  the studio and home\, and finally to the human element that connects the
 m all.\n\nWe can't wait to see you there.\n\n
