SUMMARY: Faster\, Pussycat! Kill! Kill! | Not-Quite Midnights
DESCRIPTION:Go-go dancers Varla\, Rosie\, and Billie skip out on their ni
 ghtclub jobs to race out to the desert to stir up a little mayhem. After 
 karate expert Varla kills an innocent man\, the trio takes his girlfriend
  hostage as they attempt to wheedle a hidden fortune from a misogynistic 
 old man and his muscle-bound son. A campy and exhilarating joyride\, Fast
 er\, Pussycat remains a top-tier classic of 1960s shock B-cinema. Present
 ed on 35mm from an Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences print. [83
  min\; action\, comedy\; English]
