SUMMARY: Iron Lung (2026)
DESCRIPTION:Iron Lung (2026) is a brand new American science fiction horr
 or film written\, directed\, executive produced\, edited by\, and starrin
 g Mark Fischbach (YouTuber Markiplier) in his feature directorial debut. 
 Produced and distributed by Markiplier Studios\, it is an adaptation of t
 he 2022 video game of the same name by David Szymanski\, and also stars C
 aroline Rose Kaplan\, Seán McLoughlin\, Szymanski\, Troy Baker\, Elsie Lo
 velock\, and Isaac McKee in supporting roles.\n\nThe film is set in a pos
 t-apocalyptic future after an event known as “The Quiet Rapture” caused a
 ll known stars and habitable planets in the universe to disappear. A conv
 ict (Mark Fischbach) is sent to explore an ocean of blood discovered on a
  desolate moon using a poorly constructed midget submarine nicknamed the 
 “Iron Lung”\n\nRATED: R\nLENGTH: 2hr 10mins\nFORMAT: DCP
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Film,In-Person,Tickets
