SUMMARY: Bugonia | New Americas Cinema\, Not-Quite Midnights
DESCRIPTION:Two conspiracy-obsessed young men (Jesse Plemons\, Aidan Delb
 is) kidnap the high-powered CEO of a major pharmaceutical company (Emma S
 tone)\, convinced that she is an alien intent on destroying planet Earth.
  Yorgos Lanthimos returns with an absurdist satirical comedy so maddening
 ly reflective of the current moment in its descent into hell\, you may wo
 nder if you didn't accidentally stumble into watching a documentary. [118
  min\; comedy\, drama\, sci-fi\, thriller\; English]
