SUMMARY: Haiku Tunnel | Staff Selects
DESCRIPTION:Haiku Tunnel defies comparison. A workplace comedy unlike Off
 ice Space\, based on a dramatic monologue yet nothing like the work of Sp
 alding Gray\, and featuring a neurotic lead but completely different from
  What About Bob. What Haiku Tunnel is is a deeply funny film about anxiet
 y\, work\, love\, and 17 very important letters that absolutely must go o
 ut right away (you’ll understand when you watch the movie). IU Cinema’s A
 ssistant Director of Cinema Technology Seth Mutchler says\, “Just trust m
 e!” [88 min\; comedy\; English]
