SUMMARY: Don Felder and Edwin McCain Concert
DESCRIPTION:Visit the French Lick Resort for an unforgettable evening wit
 h rock legend Don Felder and special guest Edwin McCain on Saturday March
  7th! Best known for his role as lead guitarist of the Eagles and for co-
 writing the iconic hit Hotel California\, Felder helped define the sound 
 of a generation. With a career spanning more than five decades\, he conti
 nues to captivate audiences through solo albums\, collaborations with ren
 owned artists\, and live performances around the world. This concert offe
 rs the opportunity to experience one of rock’s most influential artists a
 nd the lasting impact of his music firsthand.
