SUMMARY: 2026 Women's History Month Luncheon
DESCRIPTION:The Women’s History Month Luncheon is an opportunity to recog
 nize individual and collective accomplishments of women in the community.
  This event includes exhibitors form local women owned businesses and org
 anizations\, as well as a presentation that embodies the theme of Women’s
  History Month 2026\, “Leading the Change: Women Shaping a Sustainable Fu
 ture.” Also recognized will be the winners of the 2026 Women’s Achievemen
 t Awards.\n\nTable of 8 ticket purchasers: Please complete the registrati
 on form after the purchase is complete and before 3/17 to have your place
 ment set . CLICK HERE https://forms.gle/SDjtPSNsGiGYDX838\n\n\nALL SALES 
 END 3/17 at MIDNIGHT. Be sure to purchase before the deadline!
