SUMMARY: Banff Film Festival World Tour 2 Day Pass
DESCRIPTION:Banff Centre Mountain Film Festival World Tour is coming to B
 loomington at 7pm on March 27th and 28th\, 2026! Presenting Partners: Rab
  and Banff & Lake Louise Tourism. Brought to you by: IU Outdoor Adventure
 s.\n\nBanff Centre Mountain Film and Book Festival is one of the largest 
 and most prestigious mountain festivals in the world! Hot on the heels of
  the Festival that is held every fall in beautiful Banff\, Alberta\, the 
 Banff Centre Mountain Film Festival World Tour hits the road. With stops 
 planned in over 600 communities and more than 40 countries across the glo
 be\, the Banff World Tour celebrates amazing achievements in outdoor stor
 ytelling and filmmaking worldwide.\n\nFrom the over 400 entries submitted
  to the Festival competition each year\, award-winners and audience favor
 ites are among the films that are carefully selected to play in theatres 
 around the world. Traveling to remote vistas\, analyzing topical environm
 ental issues\, and bringing audiences up-close and personal with adrenali
 ne-packed action sports the 2025/2026 World Tour is an exhilarating and p
 rovocative exploration of the mountain world.\n\nJoin IU Outdoor Adventur
 es when Banff Centre Mountain Film Festival World Tour brings the spirit 
 of outdoor adventure to Bloomington\, at the Buskirk Chumley Theater on M
 arch 27th and 28th at 7pm (doors 6pm). Visit http://outdoors.iu.edu for f
 ilm specifics. For information contact IU Outdoor Adventures and Nicci Br
 own at brownnc@iu.edu mailto:brownnc@iu.edu\nFilm programs will be posted
  as soon as possible. Stay tuned!\n\n\nFor more information about IU Outd
 oor Adventures\, check us out at:\n http://outdoors.iu.edu\n\n@iu_outdoor
 adventures on Instagram\n\nFor more information about the Banff Centre Mo
 untain Film Festival World Tour\, check them out at:\n@BanffMtnFest\nFace
 book: BanffMountainFilmFestival\n#banffworldtour\n\n\n
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Film,Tickets,In-Person
X-TKF-FEATURED-IMAGE:https://d3flpus5evl89n.cloudfront.net/62fb9509b27fd5
 06428328ed/6980ba558a143f95459e56de/scaled_1024.jpg
