SUMMARY: Saving the Hoosier: The Concert
DESCRIPTION:This is your chance to experience Saving the Hoosier Concert 
 live\, connecting with people who care about our Hoosier National Forest 
 while you enjoy music up close. The live concert will feature Hoosier mus
 icians Sarah Flint https://www.sarahflintmusic.com/ and Jeff Shew https:/
 /jeffshewcom.wordpress.com/ \, and is a fundraiser to help complete the n
 ew documentary film “Saving the Hoosier: The Fight for America’s Forests 
 https://www.womenwithguts.com/ ”. Audience members will get to see a snea
 k peek of scenes from the film and meet narrator Hud Mellencamp https://w
 ww.imdb.com/name/nm10348731/ . While there\, enjoy some food and the oppo
 rtunity to bid on some auction items. The film is being produced by Bloom
 ington-based Women with Guts Productions https://www.womenwithguts.com/ .
 \n\nWith Artists for Climate Awareness https://artistsforclimateawareness
 .org/ as fiscal sponsor for the film\, all donations are tax-deductible. 
 Tickets for the concert are $30\, and include beverages and pizza\, gener
 ously donated by Pizza X https://www.pizzaxbloomington.com/ . Audience me
 mbers will be invited to participate in a sing-along of the Indiana state
  song\, "On the Banks of the Wabash"' that will be used in the film.\n\nB
 esides Flint and Shew\, the soundtrack for Saving the Hoosier will includ
 e music from Krista Detor https://www.kristadetor.com/ \, Carrie Newcomer
  https://www.carrienewcomer.com/ \, Charlie Jesseph https://open.spotify.
 com/artist/304dseTgiYoYhLzqcqrN4c and Busman’s Holiday https://busmanshol
 iday.bandcamp.com/album/table-talk .\n\nSaving the Hoosier follows enviro
 nmental activists who\, through grassroots education and lawsuits\, have 
 successfully protected the Hoosier National Forest from the US Forest Ser
 vice’s plans for commercial logging and prescribed burns to benefit timbe
 r sales.\n\nTickets sold in advance.\n\nSee more at https://artistsforcli
 mateawareness.org/event/saving-the-hoosier-concert/ https://artistsforcli
 mateawareness.org/event/saving-the-hoosier-concert/\n\nBuy tickets at htt
 ps://savingthehoosier.eventbrite.com https://savingthehoosier.eventbrite.
 com/
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Film,In-Person,Music,Tickets,Alliance-Center
