SUMMARY: Conclave (2024)
DESCRIPTION:CONCLAVE follows one of the world’s most secretive and ancien
 t events — selecting the new Pope. Cardinal Lawrence (Ralph Fiennes) is t
 asked with running this covert process after the unexpected death of the 
 beloved Pope. Once the Catholic Church’s most powerful leaders have gathe
 red from around the world and are locked together in the Vatican halls\, 
 Lawrence uncovers a trail of deep secrets left in the dead Pope’s wake\, 
 secrets which could shake the foundations of the Church.\n\nFORMAT: DCP\n
 LENGTH: 2h\nRATED: PG
