SUMMARY: Belt Out Loud! - Featuring Cody Ikerd and the Sidewinders
DESCRIPTION:Stone Belt is proud to announce The Sixth Annual Belt Out Lou
 d! concert\, at 7pm on May 30th. This year’s headlining performers are co
 untry music stars Cody Ikerd and the Sidewinders\, whose heartfelt songs 
 and captivating stage presence promise an unforgettable evening.\n\n\nAtt
 endees can enjoy a night of incredible music while supporting a great cau
 se. Belt Out Loud serves as a model for future events aiming to promote a
 ccessibility and inclusion for individuals of all abilities\, ensuring an
  enjoyable experience for everyone. By supporting Belt Out Loud\, attende
 es are advocating for a more inclusive society and promoting awareness ab
 out the importance of accessibility. Together\, we’ll enjoy a night of mu
 sic and pave the way for a future where every event\, big or small\, embr
 aces inclusivity as it’s core value.\n\n\nThe proceeds from the event wil
 l help Stone Belt provide vital services to individuals with developmenta
 l disabilities in our community\, including employment training\, day and
  residential services\, and advocacy support. So come out and enjoy a fan
 tastic concert while making a positive impact!\n\n\nThis event is proudly
  sponsored by IU Credit Union\, Old National Bank\, Office Easel\, Tri-Co
 unty Hydraullics\, Resource Services\, and Visit Bloomington.\n\n\nThe pr
 oceeds from your ticket will help Stone Belt provide vital services to in
 dividuals with developmental disabilities in our community\, including em
 ployment training\, day and residential services\, and advocacy support. 
 So come out and enjoy a fantastic concert while making a positive impact!
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Live,Music,Tickets
