SUMMARY: Indiana Limestone Symposium
DESCRIPTION:Sharing the art of carving the local limestone\, now in it's 
 30th year. All levels are welcome\, from professional to beginner. Carve 
 just one day or up to 2 weeks\, stone and instruction included. Held on t
 he grounds of the Bybee Stone Co\, Ellettsville.\n\nFor more information 
 and to register please visit http://www.limestonesymposium.org
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Ellettsville,Visual-Arts,Volunteer
